20	 * Description: Keyword spotting DNN model example code
21	 */
22	
23	/* Network Structure 
24	
25	  10x25 input features
26	    |
27	   IP1 : Innerproduct (weights: 250x144)
28	    |
29	   IP2 : Innerproduct (weights: 144x144)
30	    |
31	   IP3 : Innerproduct (weights: 144x144)
32	    |
33	   IP4 : Innerproduct (weights: 144x12)
34	    |
35	   12 outputs
36	
37	*/
